  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "Cth97V6+GPxGV5mDGw0yXufBTAE=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:41.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "A Powerhouse project initialized with `ph init` creates this structure:\n\n- `document-models/` - Document model implementations (schema, gen/, src/reducers, src/tests)\n- `editors/` - React editor components for document types\n- `processors/` - Event-driven components reacting to document changes\n- `subgraphs/` - Modular GraphQL services for structured data access\n\nConfiguration files:\n- `powerhouse.config.json` - Project and Vetra drive configuration\n- `powerhouse.manifest.json` - Package manifest describing contents\n- `package.json` - NPM package metadata (scoped naming: `@org-ph/package-name`)\n- `tsconfig.json` - TypeScript configuration\n- `vite.config.ts` - Build configuration\n- `vitest.config.ts` - Test configuration\n\nFor publishing, the manifest.json declares document models, editors, and their relationships (which editor serves which document type).",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:41.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:41.000Z"
    }
  },
